# ReplyGenius - Product Overview

## Product Description

ReplyGenius is a web application that helps users generate professional and contextually appropriate email replies using AI. The application analyzes incoming emails and generates 3 reply options with different tones (formal, casual, or decline) that users can choose from.

## Core Features

### 1. Landing Page
- **Purpose**: Explain the product in detail with compelling copywriting
- **Sections**:
  - Hero section with clear value proposition
  - Problem statement (user pain points)
  - Solution explanation (how the product solves problems)
  - "How It Works" section with step-by-step visuals
  - Common mistakes section (common user problems and solutions)
  - Features showcase
  - Call-to-action (CTA) to start using

### 2. Email Reply Generation
- **Input**: ChatGPT-like text input to enter the email to reply to
- **Output**: 3 reply options with different tones:
  - **Formal**: Professional and official language
  - **Casual**: Relaxed and friendly language
  - **Decline**: Polite and professional rejection
- **Tone Selector**: Users can select tone before generation or change tone after generation

### 3. History & Chat Management
- **Chat History**: Save all generated replies
- **History View**: List of all previous conversations/generations
- **Re-generate**: Ability to regenerate with different tones

### 4. Authentication & Usage Limits
- **Guest Mode**:
  - No login required
  - Can generate up to 3 times
  - History not permanently saved (localStorage)
  
- **Gmail OAuth Login**:
  - Login using Google OAuth
  - Can generate 10 times per week
  - History saved in cloud
  - Limit resets every week

### 5. User Experience
- **Simple but Attractive UI**: Minimalist yet appealing design
- **Responsive Design**: Works well on desktop and mobile
- **Real-time Generation**: Feedback while AI is generating
- **Copy to Clipboard**: Easy copy of generated results to clipboard

## Common User Problems & Solutions

### Problem 1: Writing Email Replies Takes Too Much Time
**Solution**: AI generates 3 options in seconds, users just need to choose and edit if needed

### Problem 2: Confused About Choosing the Right Tone
**Solution**: Tone selector with preview, users can try various tones and choose the most appropriate one

### Problem 3: Email Replies Too Formal or Too Casual
**Solution**: 3 options with different tones allow users to choose the most appropriate one for the context

### Problem 4: Forgot Previous Email Context
**Solution**: Chat history allows users to view all previous generations

### Problem 5: Unsure How to Decline Politely
**Solution**: Special "Decline" tone to help write professional and polite rejections

## Target Users

- Professionals who receive many emails
- Freelancers who need quick replies
- Business owners who want to increase productivity
- Anyone who wants to improve email communication quality
